home.description: Homesite #7Enjoy the holidays in a new home with views of the sparkling lights overlooking Chino Hills into Chino Valley! This home offers charming outdoor living including a courtyard accessible through bi-fold doors at the parlour, a sliding door at kitchen, as well as a private backyard. The state of the art kitchen features GE&nbsp;Caf&eacute; stainless steel appliances including refrigerator, white Euro-style raised panel cabintery, as well as upgraded granite countertops and full backsplash. The luxurious master bath has a 6' soaking tub and upgraded countertops. This move-in ready home also includes designer selected flooring throughout and Nexia, a home automation system that can be controlled by your smart device!&nbsp;

Homesite #18This stunning, brand new home has views of the rolling hills in a prime northern Chino Hills location within an award-winning school district. Spacious home with kitchen island, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, classic white Thermofoil cabinets and Subway tile with a full backsplash. Striking easy-care wood inspired laminate flooring throughout the main living level and designer-selected carpet is in all bedrooms. The master suite has dual sinks and a 6 ft. soaking bath tub to relax in at the end of the day. Each bedroom has a private bath and this floor plan has a large bonus room upstairs.&nbsp;

Homesite #6This home offers gorgeous views of the Chino Valley and Corona, while being within close proximity to area schools and shopping. Homeowners will be greeted by an elegant curved entry and staircase that leads to both a parlor and dining room. Home amenities include a courtyard, fully landscaped backyard, and Nexia, a home automation system with "keyless" entrypad, thermostat, lamp and appliance control, and an exterior camera that can all be operated by your smart device. The stunning kitchen features GE Monogram&nbsp;Caf&eacute; stainless steel appliances including refrigerator, white thermafoil raised panel cabinets, upgraded granite countertops and full custom backsplash. The master bathroom has a 6' soaking tub and beautiful upgraded countertops. Designer selected flooring has been selected throughout including laminate, ceramic tile and upgraded carpet.

Homesite #15 End the year in a new home! This peaceful neighborhood has nearby natural open spaces and hiking trails, and the back yard is landscaped with northern views of rolling hills. Grand circular entry is sure to impress with a parlor off to the side, as well as dining room. This move-in ready home includes an elegant tile backsplash at kitchen, wood inspired low-maintenance laminate flooring throughout the main living level and enhanced carpet in all bedrooms and parlor. The impressive open design flows into the family room, kitchen with island and a nook. A dramatic curved staircase lands at a loft area useful for a tech desk, and there is a large laundry room with a sink.

Homesite #16With this upscale spacious new home you will get one lower level bedroom as well as three upper level bedrooms with en suite bath, high ceilings and doorways throughout. We include many top quality "must see" amenities such as the Nexia Home Intelligence System with keyless entry touch pad, thermostat, and outdoor rated infrared camera, and more. The kitchen and master bathroom have crisp white Thermofoil cabinets with the soft-close drawer/door feature, and come with a solid-surface countertop. Included is a beautiful backsplash at kitchen as well as easy-care wood inspired laminate flooring throughout the main living areas on the first level. Designer-selected carpeting is in all bedrooms. Balcony off master bedroom. Landscaping is being installed now and will be completed before you move in!&nbsp;

community.name: Desert Ridge
community.description: Grand Opening underway! Ask about generous Grand Opening Specials that are available now. Desert Ridge is located in Canyon Crest, a master planned community nestled in the ridges of Mesquite, Nevada and near the Oasis Golf Club. Four distinctive floor plans with open concept layout and great room, covered rear patio, den and optional second level with bonus room or loft, offers a very desirable and affordable lifestyle opportunity. An extended 3rd space garage option is offered, per plan!

home.description: Homesite #52This beautiful single level residence includes a great room, large corner lot and rear covered patio along with many other upgrades and appointments. Plus it is Energy Star&reg; certified! Call to see today!

Homesite #45 - MLS # 1115244 Grand Opening Special! The current sales price of $212,177 already has a $10,000 incentive applied. This Move In Ready Home is now available in the brand new community of Desert Ridge in Canyon Crest. There is still time to personalize this home with a variety of selections and other upgrades available at the design center. It already includes designer-selected flooring, and an upgraded appliance package. Offering the best of both worlds, this brand new home is nearly move-in ready with an opportunity to customize/personalize.&nbsp; It features two bedrooms and two bathrooms. An open floor plan includes spacious living room and kitchen with stainless steel appliances and elegant maple cabinets for your entertainment and enjoyment. It includes beautiful designer selected 20"x20" ceramic tile in entry, kitchen, great room and other locations, and upgraded carpeting in bedrooms.&nbsp; This home is Energy Star certified, which translates to energy efficiency and lower utilities. Low HOA dues and close to the Oasis Canyons and Oasis Palmer golf courses as well as shopping and gaming. There are seven golf courses within 10 minutes of your new home! Las Vegas is just a short 80 miles away, and St. George is just 36 miles away. In one hour you can be on Lake Mead. Mesquite residents enjoy 330 days of sunshine, walking paths and bike paths. Mesquite has one of the lowest tax rates in Nevada.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

Homesite #70This move in ready home is nearing completion but there is still time to personalize it to suit your tastes and lifestyle. It includes a great room, rear covered patio and many sophisticated appointments and it is Energy Star&reg; certified! Call to tour today.

community.name: Trellis at Esencia
community.description: Here you will discover a charming collection of Farmhouse-style residences that evoke the essence of early South Orange County living, which has inspired the village of Esencia in Rancho Mission Viejo. Front porches, friendly white picket fences, covered decks, optional rooftop decks, and rear garages with alley access define these inviting residences with private yards that are situated around six home paseos. From home, you will be just a short stroll to a park, K-8 school and a proposed daycare center. Trellises dot the landscape here which includes aromatic citrus trees, roses and even an edible garden. Everywhere you look, good stuff is growing at Trellis at Esencia. Grand Opening under way!
